04:56.830 --> 04:59.474
But on the night that Jesus was betrayed,

05:00.610 --> 05:04.334
He was spending time with his disciples, sharing a meal together.

05:05.416 --> 05:12.685
And what's wild to think about is that he knew that their faith would be tested, that they'd be scattered.

05:14.266 --> 05:20.914
He knew that somebody was going to deny him and another one of his disciples was going to completely betray him.

05:20.934 --> 05:26.741
And yet in that moment, he chose to express his love for them and serve them.

05:28.804 --> 05:30.546
And so he took bread and he broke it.

05:31.810 --> 05:34.173
