05:42.244 --> 05:46.891
And he said, this is my blood shed for the sacrifice for you.

05:48.613 --> 06:00.850
And so he says, when we eat this bread and drink of this cup, that we'd remember the sacrifice that he made for us to experience freedom, to experience life, to experience forgiveness of sins.

06:01.442 --> 06:05.126
