06:31.266 --> 06:34.832
as you reflect and pause in these next few moments.

06:34.852 --> 06:40.542
I just want to challenge you to think about, is there something you need to throw off in your life?

06:42.425 --> 06:44.269
Is there a sin that you need to confess?

06:44.329 --> 06:46.933
Is there a grudge that you've been holding?

06:46.953 --> 06:52.162
Is there somebody that's hurt you that you need to forgive or ask God to help you forgive?

06:52.182 --> 06:56.530
Or maybe you need to ask the Spirit to renew or change something in you.

06:58.050 --> 07:10.410
Take these next few moments as we continue on in worship to think about that, to pray about that, to confess that to God, ask Him to help you put on the new self that only comes to Jesus Christ.

