Our faith hinges on the resurrection.

07:22.309 --> 07:25.234
It hinges on what Jesus did for us.

07:26.978 --> 07:28.301
And so we're going to remember that.

07:28.882 --> 07:34.793
We're going to be grateful for that and ask God for him to come in and move in our lives and our hearts.

07:35.795 --> 07:41.746
So when you're ready, you can open up those elements and receive communion and the band will stand us in just a few moments for this next song.

