God, that we can step foot in here and know that you see us, you love us, and that we have a living hope in you when we place our hope and our future in you.

19:08.869 --> 19:10.731
God, that you are here waiting for us.

19:11.752 --> 19:15.557
Lord Jesus, we need more of you in our life, and that's what we ask for.

19:15.617 --> 19:16.337
