54:13.230 --> 54:15.533
And they would be given an opportunity to respond to Him.

54:18.437 --> 54:19.739
God, go before us right now.

54:19.780 --> 54:21.522
Go before us in those conversations.

54:21.602 --> 54:24.647
Soften that person's heart so they'd be open to saying yes.

54:25.829 --> 54:28.613
Prepare their hearts right now for what they're gonna hear next week.

